   <name>Small Craft Advisory issued November 15 at 6:31PM EST until November 18 at 7:00AM EST by NWS Caribou ME</name>
   <styleUrl>#sev_minor</styleUrl>
   <Style>
    <BalloonStyle />
   </Style>
   <Snippet>* WHAT...West winds 15 to 25 kt with gusts up to 30 kt and seas
3 to 5 ft expected.

* WHERE...Intra Coastal Waters from Schoodic Point, ME to
Stonington, ME.

* WHEN...From 7 PM Sunday to 7 AM EST Tuesday.

* IMPACTS...Conditions will be hazardous to small craft.</Snippet>
